    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are hotlines. i've looked. but those people just follow a script to keep you alive so you can keep suffering. what's the point? i spend every day just trying to get through the next hour, and then the next, and it's just... it's a cycle of nothing. honestly, sometimes it feels like the only way to actually find some peace is to just stop fighting it entirely. does that even make sense?",
